import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='speed', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['speed'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Mean: {data['speed'].mean():.2f}")
    plt.axvline(data['speed'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Median: {data['speed'].median():.2f}")
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wind speed?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Wind Speed (m/s)')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 8))
    heatmap = sns.kdeplot(data=data, x="longitude", y="latitude", hue="speed", cmap="coolwarm", shade=True, shade_lowest=False)
    heatmap.set(xlabel='Longitude', ylabel='Latitude')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wind vectors across the latitude and longitude?')
    plt.legend(title='Wind Speed (m/s)', loc='lower right', bbox_to_anchor=(1.25, 0.0), ncol=1)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 8))
    heatmap = sns.heatmap(data.pivot_table(index='latitude', columns='longitude', values='speed'), cmap='coolwarm', annot=True, fmt=".2f", cbar_kws={'label': 'Wind Speed (m/s)'})
    heatmap.set_xlabel('Longitude')
    heatmap.set_ylabel('Latitude')
    heatmap.set_title('What is the distribution of wind speed across the latitude and longitude?')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
